    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-02-17T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-02-17T08:00:00-05:00" n="391"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d391">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/4254: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Shanghai (<persName corresp="#p_CES1"
                            type="from">Cunningham</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Shanghai</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-02-17T21:00:00+08:00"
                            >February 17, 1932—9 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 17—11:10 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>65. Japanese Consul <persName corresp="#p_IS1">Iguchi</persName> stated tonight
                    that the Consulate General expected momentarily from Tokyo terms of an ultimatum
                    requiring the immediate cessation of hostilities and withdrawal on the part of
                    Chinese Army; that the Japanese Consul would immediately deliver same to Mayor
                    and Japanese Army commander to Chinese Army commander. <persName
                        corresp="#p_IS1">Iguchi</persName> opined that the ultimatum would be
                    delivered tonight and 24 [hours?] would be given for compliance.</p>
                <p>Repeated to the Legation and Nanking.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_CES1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cunningham</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
